Package Locomotive

Class Train

java.lang.Object
Superclass.Vehicle
WheeledVehicle.WheeledTransportation
Locomotive.Train
Direct Known Subclasses:
Metro
public class Train
extends WheeledTransportation
The Train class is designed to contain the most basic attributes/methods which any train should possess.
Author:
Kevin Courey
